data.description: MOVE-IN-READY HOME!  ***MOTIVATED SELLER*** Seller is leaving all wall decor, TV's, washer/dryer, refrigerator (inside and garage), furniture (except for bedroom set in bedroom #2 and work/office equipment in bedroom #3) and patio furniture. This 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom, 2-car garage, 1,487 square foot home is perfect for entertaining your family and friends. As soon as you walk in, you are greeted by tall ceilings and tons of natural light. Just off the entryway you will find the laundry room and a closet for all of your storage needs. As you continue down the hallway, you will enter the kitchen, living room, and dining room. This beautiful kitchen offers floor-to-ceiling white cabinets, granite countertops, a large center island, and stainless steel appliances. Off of the kitchen you will find access to both secondary bedrooms and a shared bathroom. Towards the back of the living room there are entrances to both the backyard and the owner's suite. In the backyard you have a covered patio, perfect for grilling and watching the beautiful Texas sunsets. In the owner's suite there will be double doors leading to a luxurious and relaxing bathroom, complete with double vanities and a large walk-in shower. In the bedroom you will also find a walk-in closet just waiting for you to fill it.
